<Class name="CM_CashPayment" id="f25200fc-3f83-4966-86e0-2d0e49587bea">
    <superclass name="CM_Cash"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>
***  Cash that has been allocated from the cash receipt to the Cargo / Invoice.
	 If myInvoice is populated represents a real transaction, i.e. payment of an existing charge.
	 Else if proformaDesc is populated represents an allocation of the cash receipt total for expected extra charges before the cargo is released
	 (typically handling charges and storage).
	 If its a pro forma, it will be converted into a real payment and deleted when the real transaction occurs.
	 Payments are per invoice line from 8.3.1, and also held against the invoice, tracked item and cash receipt.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="cashPayment"/>
